==Russian==
[[Category:Russian nouns]]
===Noun===
'''юг''' (jug) {{m}}, (only ''singular'', ''plural'' form is colloquial)

# [[south]] 
#* {{RUchar|Уехать на юга́}} ''(colloquial) &mdash; To go to the south (e.g., to the Black Sea coast) for holiday.''
# [[South]] &mdash; southern part of any region
#* {{RUchar|жить на юге}} &mdash; ''to live in the South (of Russia)''
# ''(obsolete)'' [[southerly]] [[wind]], {{RUchar|[[южный|ю́жный]] [[ветер|ве́тер]]}}
#* {{RUchar|юг веет, старого греет}} &mdash; ''A south wind blows, it warms an old man.''

